        <p>This Cookie Policy explains how Popcart uses cookies and similar technologies to recognize you when you visit our website or use our platform.</p>
        
        <h3>What Are Cookies?</h3>
        <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help websites recognize users and remember preferences.</p>
        
        <h3>How We Use Cookies</h3>
        <p>We use cookies for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for the platform to function (e.g., login functionality).</li>
            <li><strong>Performance Cookies:</strong> Track usage and help improve the website and app</li>
            <li><strong>Functional Cookies:</strong> Remember user preferences, such as language settings,products of interest.</li>
            <li><strong>Targeting Cookies:</strong> Used for personalized advertisements and analytics.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Managing Cookies</h3>
        <p>You can manage, disable, or delete cookies through your browser settings. However, disabling cookies may impact the functionality of the platform.</p>

